{"tid":764442,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"點解成日窮人成日扮有錢 中產/有錢人就唔識用錢","createTime":"2018-08-02T03:54:02.000Z","updateTime":"2018-08-02T04:19:18.000Z","uid":95060,"like":2,"dislike":19,"uniUserReply":5,"replies":[{"pid":"8016d29185d029e6fcae973cd63a7cb528b92196","tid":764442,"uid":95060,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-02T03:54:02.000Z","msg":"講緊中學果時。<br />\n<br />\n有班同學係IG就成日POST去食好野，去旅行，買新鞋新衫，好識享受生活<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wink.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n但就住共屋<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n相反，有D FD就出得街都係果幾件U記衫，<br />\n淨係識留係屋企(打機)同落街打波 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n成班約出街又會諗住計住用左幾錢 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n但去過佢地屋企先知原來係貴樓/連屋打通<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n點解世界要對人咁唔公平，<br />\n富有人格就要生係一個窮人家庭，<br />\n窮撚人格就生係一個富人家庭<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n#LIKE <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/like.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />  有錢唔用傻過鳩<br />\n#DISLIKE <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dislike.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />  老母家教好，有錢冇煩惱"},{"pid":"06f6ebd9f960a65e9a11df647d8f66a3666c97c7","tid":764442,"uid":36296,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-02T03:57:43.000Z","msg":"就係因為佢地慳 先會累積財富囉戇鳩"},{"pid":"a11eb5814b248bd9813441df26f8d3c1a19ae67e","tid":764442,"uid":10442,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-08-02T04:01:47.000Z","msg":"因為窮人成日俾人睇唔起, 自卑, 咪想充大頭, 刷存在感, 想有人認同自己<br />\n中產/有錢人本身就有錢, 駛乜理人點睇自己"},{"pid":"efcecf2a7f2de6bdbd23b50e5ecc2351b8e977d3","tid":764442,"uid":95060,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"a11eb5814b248bd9813441df26f8d3c1a19ae67e","tid":764442,"uid":10442,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-08-02T04:01:47.000Z","msg":"因為窮人成日俾人睇唔起, 自卑, 咪想充大頭, 刷存在感, 想有人認同自己<br />\n中產/有錢人本身就有錢, 駛乜理人點睇自己"},"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"20